{
  "name": "AutoFilter",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.AutoFilter\">AutoFilter</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 对象。使用 <strong>Filters</strong> 属性可返回由各个列筛选组成的集合。使用 <strong>Range</strong> 属性可返回代表整个筛选区域的 <strong>Range</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>要为工作表创建 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 对象，必须手动打开或使用 <strong>Range</strong> 对象的 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 方法打开工作表上某个区域上的自动筛选功能。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例存储当前筛选的地址和筛选条件，然后应用新筛选器。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> w = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> autoFilter = w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> currentFiltRange = autoFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filters = autoFilter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filterArray = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Array</span>(w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; filterArray.<span class=\"hljs-property\">length</span>; i++) {\n        filterArray[i] = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Array</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> f = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; f &lt;= filters.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; f++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filter = filters.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(f)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>) {\n            filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span>) {\n                filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span>\n                filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria2</span>\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    w.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFilter</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;apple&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使用filterArray数组来为第一张工作表恢复最初的自动筛选。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> w = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> currentFiltRange = w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filters = w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filterArray = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Array</span>(w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; filterArray.<span class=\"hljs-property\">length</span>; i++) {\n        filterArray[i] = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Array</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> f = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; f &lt;= filters.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; f++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> filter = filters.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(f)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>) {\n            filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span>) {\n                filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span>\n                filterArray[f][<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>] = filter.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria2</span>\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    w.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> col = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; col &lt; filterArray.<span class=\"hljs-property\">length</span>; col++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] !== <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]) {\n                w.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(currentFiltRange).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFilter</span>(col, filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>], filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>], filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>])\n            } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n                w.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(currentFiltRange).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFilter</span>(col, filterArray[col][<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>])\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表对指定工作表的自动筛选。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong> 对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FilterMode",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果工作表的筛选模式为自动筛选，则返回 <strong>True</strong>。只读 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的筛选模式是否为自动筛选。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FilterMode</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示判断第一张工作表的筛选模式是否为自动筛选，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表的筛选模式是自动筛选&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表的筛选模式不是自动筛选&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Filters",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Filters</strong> 集合，该集合表示自动筛选区域中的所有筛选器。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将变量设置为第一张工作表上的筛选区域中第一列的筛选的 Criteria1 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">On</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> c1 = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Criteria1</span>\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上自动筛选中应用的筛选器数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Filters</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Filters",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Range",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Range</strong> 对象，它代表应用指定的“自动筛选”的区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例将应用第一张工作表的“自动筛选”的地址保存在变量中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> address = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例滚动工作簿窗口，直至自动筛选应用到的区域位于活动窗口的左上角。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> range = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ScrollRow</span> = range.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Row</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ScrollColumn</span> = range.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Column</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Sort",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>获取 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 集合的排序列和排序次序。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的 AutoFilter 集合排序方向是否为 xlSortColumns。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> == xlSortColumns)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的 AutoFilter 集合的排序方式设置为区分大小写的排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MatchCase</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Sort",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "ApplyFilter",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>应用指定的 <strong>Autofilter</strong> 对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例应用活动工作表的 AutoFilter 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ApplyFilter</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例应用第一张工作表的 AutoFilter 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ApplyFilter</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "ShowAllData",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>显示 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 对象返回的所有数据。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例展示活动工作表 AutoFilter 对象返回的所有数据。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ShowAllData</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示判断如果第一张工作表的筛选模式为自动筛选，则显示所有数据，即清除所有筛选条件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FilterMode</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoFilter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ShowAllData</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}